latestIgtvVideos.title: CTM For Healthy Skin with @perennecosmetics
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Product Include In Kit: Nourishing Cleansing Cream (95ml), Perenne Moisturising Cream (50 gm), Perenne Revitalizing Tonic Mist (100 ml) 
--
This is a silicon-free daily regime for all skin types(except acne-prone skin). When this CTM is used regularly, it will restore and refine skin texture, reduce dullness and enhance glow, making you look youthful.
Perenne Nourishing Cleansing Cream: Deeply cleanses the skin and leaving it soft and supple.
Perenne Revitalizing Tonic Mist: It finely tones up the skin, balancing ph level and minimizes pores.
Perenne Moisturizing cream: It's silicone-free, Shea butter based, very light in texture, it quickly absorbs into skin making it soft and supple.
Perenne CTM being chemical-free don't let make up turn cakey or black when used as a pre-makeup base.
It is silicone-free so best for post makeup care as it lets your skin cells breathe and enhance skin cell rejuvenation.
It is enriched with the goodness of kiwi extract, grapefruit extract, white mulberry extract, green tea extract and many other botanical extracts.
